Detailed Description

Container class for all certificates on the card.

be.belgium.eid.BEID_Certificates.BEID_Certificates (  ) 

Create a BEID_Certificates store without any link to a card.

This store is not linked to any card, therefore some methods can not be used and throw a BEID_ExBadUsage exception.
